caption:
We are excited to announce our ablative laser resurfacing course at @fordplasticsurgery on Toronto May 3, 2025.  This is one of our favourite courses to run.  We teach participants how to maximize the use of the Sciton erbium lasers with both full field laser resurfacing and profractional resurfacing.  This course is for advanced laser specialists who want to add surgical laser resurfacing to their practice.  This is a great course for providers and for modern facial rejuvenation, it is a must!
